                    <Footer/>
                    <WebAddress>https://vault.fbi.gov</WebAddress>
                </FooterDetails>
                <Header/>
                <Paragraph>The FBI's electronic FOIA library, which contains nearly 7,000 documents and other media that have been scanned from paper and made into more accessible digital copies, is named the "Vault." The library includes new files that have been released to the public, but never added to the FBI website; dozens of records previously posted on the FBI website, but removed when requests diminished; files from the previous FBI FOIA Library; and new and previously unreleased files.</Paragraph>
